== 衝撞 ==
当地时间14时许，一名男子在[[特里尔|特里尔]]的一条街道上驾车冲撞行人，造成5人死亡，至少30人受伤。死者中包括一名婴儿和一名幼童。肇事者是特里爾一名51岁的男子，事發後該男子被逮捕。据悉，肇事车辆为一辆深灰色[[路虎攬勝|路虎攬勝]]，当时正在高速行驶。司机血液中的酒精含量很高<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55148518 |title=Trier: Five die as car ploughs through Germany pedestrian zone |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207041410/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55148518 |dead-url=no|work=BBC News }}</ref>。

== 嫌疑犯 ==
经查明，袭击者是一名51岁的德国籍的特里爾男子，在袭击发生4分钟后被捕。据报道，他在事发前喝了很多酒。警方怀疑，行凶者肇事動機并非出于政治、宗教或意识形态，事故發生的原因很有可能是嫌犯患有精神健康问题以及酗酒。同時有一名医生也認為该男子可能患有精神疾病，所以嫌疑犯在接受警方审讯时還将接受心理检查<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/trier-germany-car-kills-injures-pedestrians/#app |title=German man arrested after driving car into crowd, killing 5 |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201172019/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/trier-germany-car-kills-injures-pedestrians/#app |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://luxtimes.lu/european-union/42427-driver-kills-five-in-trier-attack-may-have-mental-problems |title=Driver kills five in Trier attack, may have mental problems |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202075619/https://luxtimes.lu/european-union/42427-driver-kills-five-in-trier-attack-may-have-mental-problems |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

